{"tid":1787013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"康文署疑以版權為由打壓資訊自由 九鐵特藏不能直接從網上瀏覽","createTime":"2019-12-17T14:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T05:58:14.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4cc244e6c4db925d99b67f7bf8fe303b8711890","tid":1787013,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/79272073_1233905596804365_4285172717570752512_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ohc=PLiPil2wAjoAQmDIpIs-n6f1AukqzbqUJGBDbxWT60c4bf0_9t-bwj-aQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=3b747fd3976b9b2b3a93c429bec961ed&amp;oe=5E7DCF89\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F79272073_1233905596804365_4285172717570752512_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_ohc%3DPLiPil2wAjoAQmDIpIs-n6f1AukqzbqUJGBDbxWT60c4bf0_9t-bwj-aQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D3b747fd3976b9b2b3a93c429bec961ed%26oe%3D5E7DCF89&h=2b75fec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當外國政府和公共圖書館對歷史資訊採用開放和自由的版權，任何人都可以在不同地方查閱和分享，甚至可作商業用時，香港政府卻對版權越來越著緊。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以往可以在家中查看的九廣鐵路年報，今日發現只能在圖書館內瀏覽。</span></strong>目的是不想你可以cap圖，去分享和了解屬於自己居住地方的發展史。<br />\n<br />\n而市政局，區域市政局，以至各個政府和公營機構（如房屋署，土地發展公司和地鐵公司等）在2005年之前的年報也應該放在多媒體資訊系統，任由市民（包括海外人土）查閱和分享，而不是只限在圖書館內瀏覽。因為這些資訊財產權是屬於大家每一個人，公眾有權自由使用它們。但相信香港政府一定不會這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/kc-railway-collection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmis.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fkc-railway-collection&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2ButVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=bd9ef2de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/kc-railway-collection</a><br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkplanninginfo/photos/a.132297946965141/1233905590137699/?type=3&amp;av=131455797049356&amp;eav=AfZgbjU1VEMp6ExHGMNSKIR5N76IcZTYg6woqk5BEP-ZxW6qsPxymU8vGMRHOGv3qaw&amp;theater&not;if_t=page_post_reaction&not;if_id=1576570228701828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkplanninginfo%2Fphotos%2Fa.132297946965141%2F1233905590137699%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26av%3D131455797049356%26eav%3DAfZgbjU1VEMp6ExHGMNSKIR5N76IcZTYg6woqk5BEP-ZxW6qsPxymU8vGMRHOGv3qaw%26theater%C2%ACif_t%3Dpage_post_reaction%C2%ACif_id%3D1576570228701828&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2ButVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=77871bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkplanninginfo/photos/a.132297946965141/1233905590137699/?type=3&amp;av=131455797049356&amp;eav=AfZgbjU1VEMp6ExHGMNSKIR5N76IcZTYg6woqk5BEP-ZxW6qsPxymU8vGMRHOGv3qaw&amp;theater&not;if_t=page_post_reaction&not;if_id=1576570228701828</a>"},{"pid":"fae26d102f53443ad86c32eb736cd802605682ac","tid":1787013,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb60a210cb914faa369fa0b5e79d98a5c8287788","tid":1787013,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}